~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        A Distributed Load Generator for Membase and Elastic Couchbase
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Building:
	
	ant build

Running:

	ant run
	
	This will start the load generator on a single node. The load generator
	will attempt to cluster together with other servers on the same subnet.
	In order to setup and run a load test use the rest api.